pricing_analysis.trend: Aggressive price compression defines the market, with new flagship models (GPT-4o, Claude 3.5 Sonnet) offering significantly better price-performance than predecessors. A clear bifurcation is emerging: premium subscriptions for power users seeking all-in-one access, and an ultra-competitive, low-cost token market for developers, driven by open-source models and new entrants from China like DeepSeek.
